snippet: Richard Dare, the chief executive and managing director of the Brooklyn Philharmonic, will leave to become president and chief executive of the New Jersey Symphony Orchestra in January.
abstract: Richard Dare, the chief executive and managing director of the Brooklyn Philharmonic, will leave to become president and chief executive of the New Jersey Symphony Orchestra in January.

headline.main: Contra N.B.A.: Orchestra Executive Moves from Brooklyn to New Jersey
headline.print_headline: Orchestra Chief’s Move: Brooklyn to New Jersey
